{
  "stem": "1160.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my mother-- grandmother was wearing long skirt.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] She always wore long clothes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she was very worried and she was always telling my mother in Yiddish, my child, put me down.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just leave me here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm already-- you can't do anything with me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You just go, hold the children.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my mother was crying.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she says, mother, don't tell me this, because I'm not going to put you down and I'm not going to leave you anywhere.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Long as I can carry you, I'm going to carry you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But my grandmother was very worried.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So then she-- she said to us, the three of us in the back, she says, you hold onto my skirt.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And each time I call your names, that person who is called, you have to give a tug on the skirt so I can feel it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And each time she was saying the names-- our names-- we tugged so she knew that we are there, because she couldn't turn back.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was-- she was helpless.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my mother, she was also, are you here?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Are you here?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But there was already not much energy to do much more than just to carry her.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And this is one picture what I remember.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then my grandmother was taken from us again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We arrived to a place-- and she was taken.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The sick was taken away from us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we arrive into a-- we arrive after Gostling--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we find grandmother a few-- one more time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We find her in St.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Valentin.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] When we arrived to St.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Valentin, this was a lovely, lovely place.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
